name: Customized Monogram Necklace
description:
Such a wonderful item to have as a personal keepsake or to give to a special family member or friend.  Either way, you'll smile each time you look at this specialty hand crafted piece made of precious metals.  

You can choose which metal and the size you'd like your necklace to be.  Gold vermeil is sterling silver dipped in 14kt gold.  Each unique piece is hand cut, it takes about 3-4 weeks for delivery from start to arriving at your doorstep.  Because there are no two alike, refunds are not offered for this item.

**Please include your chain style and initials in the order which you would like them to be on the necklace in the comments section in PayPal.**
